quran[32]{c,v,t}:
  86,1,aasman aur raat ke waqt anay walay ki qasam
  86,2,aur tum kokiya maloom ke raat ke waqt anay walakiya hai
  86,3,woh tara hai chamaknay wala
  86,4,ke koi mutnaqas nahi jis par nigehbaan muqarrar nahi
  86,5,to ensaan ko dekhna chahiye ke woh kaahe se peda howa hai
  86,6,woh uchaltay hue pani se peda howa hai
  86,7,jo peeth aur seenay ke beech mein se nikalta hai
  86,8,be shak khuda is ke a'aday ( yani phir peda karne ) par Qadir hai
  86,9,jis din dilon ke bhaid jacchay jayen ge
  86,10,to ensaan ki kuch paish nah chal sakay gi aur nah koi is ka madadgaar ho ga
  86,11,aasman ki qasam jo meen barsata hai
  86,12,aur zameen ki qasam jo phatt jati hai
  86,13,ke yeh kalaam ( haq ko baatil se ) judda karne wala hai
  86,14,aur behooda baat nahi hai
  86,15,yeh log to apni tdbiron mein lag rahay hain
  86,16,aur hum apni tadbeer kar rahay hain
  86,17,to tum kafiroon ko mohlat do bas chand roz hi mohlat do
  87,1,( ae paighambar ) apne perwar-digaar jallel al shan ke naam ki tasbeeh karo
  87,2,jis ne ( ensaan ko ) banaya phir ( is ke aaza ko ) durustkiya
  87,3,aur jis ne ( is ka ) andaza t_hraya ( phir is ko ) rasta bataya
  87,4,aur jis ne charah ugaya
  87,5,phir is ko siyah rang ka kora kar diya
  87,6,hum tumhe parha den ge ke tum faramosh nah karo ge
  87,7,magar jo khuda chahay. woh khuli baat ko bhi jaanta hai aur chhupi ko bhi
  87,8,hum tum ko aasaan tareeqay ki tofeq den ge
  87,9,so jahan taq nasiyaat ( ke ) nafea ( honay ki umeed ) ho nasiyaat karte raho
  87,10,jo khauf rakhta hai woh to nasiyaat pakdae ga
  87,11,aur ( be khauf ) badbakht pehlu tehi kere ga
  87,12,jo ( qayamat ko ) barri ( taiz ) aag mein daakhil ho ga
  87,13,phir wahan nah marey ga aur nah jiye ga
  87,14,be shak woh morad ko poanch gaya jo pak howa
  87,15,aur apne perwar-digaar ke naam ka zikar karta raha aur namaz parhta raha
